OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny showers
OL,6,Fat first will soon fade out to leave a
OL,7,Flargely dry evening with late sunny
OL,8,Fspells, but soon turning cloudy as
OL,9,Frain spreads into eastern parts. Low
OL,10,Fcloud and heavy rain then spreading to
OL,11,Fall areas overnight.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FA wet start to the day with
OL,14,Frain and drizzle. Rain easing in the
OL,15,Fmorning to leave a breezy and cloudy
OL,16,Fday with just the odd outbreak of
OL,17,Flight rain.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
