OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and breezy on Friday with a few
OL,7,Fshowers possible. Drier with sunny
OL,8,Fspells on Saturday. Dry on Sunday with
OL,9,Fhazy sunshine developing.
